The Herald Prosper Dembedza Court Correpondent Harare provincial magistrate Mrs Vongai Muchuchuti Guwuriro has granted $10 000 bail to a Sasai employee who allegedly defrauded a commodity broker Simon Seven of his 1,2 million rand in botched cash tranfer deal. Tapuwa Dikanifuniwa, was ordered to report once a month at Avondale police in Harare and to stay at his given address. He was also ordered not to interfere with witnesses until the matter is finalised.